<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/656176-for-those-who-know-the-story-of-jeffery">For those who know the story of Jeffery McDonald and have read the book, what were your opinions on the book? Did it follow the story as you know it?
 Anyone who can give me any information, I would really appreciate it. Thanks.</a>
